  "description": "<div id=\"product-detail\">\n\n    <h4>Application:</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>2007-2016 Mini Cooper S / JCW with 1.6L l4 GAS DOHC Turbocharged Engine</li>\n        <li>2007-2016 Mini Cooper S Clubman / JCW Clubman with 1.6L l4 GAS DOHC Turbocharged Engine</li>\n        <li>2012-2015 Mini Cooper Roadster S / Roadster JCW with 1.6L l4 GAS DOHC Turbocharged Engine</li>\n        <li>2011-2016 Mini Cooper Countryman S / JCW with 1.6L l4 GAS DOHC Turbocharged Engine</li>\n        <li>2013-2016 Mini Cooper Paceman S / JCW with 1.6L l4 GAS DOHC Turbocharged Engine</li>\n        <li>2011-2016 Peugeot RCZ with 1.6L l4 GAS DOHC Turbocharged Engine</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"color:red;\"><em>*The diameter of the oil return line hole is approximately 18.2 mm. Please confirm your stock size before ordering, or prepare for any necessary oil return line modifications.</em></p>\n\n    <h4>Features:</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>High quality replacements for factory parts; excellent durability, optimizing vehicle performance</li>\n        <li>OE design; simple replacement for factory part</li>\n        <li>Center rotating bearing housing designed to work with factory oil and coolant lines; turbo boost control solenoid valve included</li>\n        <li>Component dynamically balanced using state-of-the-art balancing machine (avg 0.5 mg or less)</li>\n        <li>Turbine housing made from ductile iron QT450-10, withstand temperatures up to 700¡ãC</li>\n        <li>Steel turbine wheel made from K418 alloy for high oxidation resistance and stability up to 900¡ãC</li>\n        <li>Cast aluminium blades with good air tightness and corrosion resistance</li>\n        <li>Accessories included</li>\n        <li>1 year warranty for manufacturing defects</li>\n        <li style=\"color:red;\"><em>Professional installation is highly recommended</em></li>\n        <li style=\"color:red;\"><em>Before installing the turbocharger, analyze and eliminate the cause of the previous failure (e.g., insufficient oil supply, foreign bodies in intake, crankcase ventilation issues, etc.)</em></li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h4>Technical Specifications:</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Durable Compressor Wheel: 12(6+6) blades, Size: 41*54 mm</li>\n        <li>Turbine Wheel: 11 blades, Size: 40.5*45 mm</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h4>Turbo Part Numbers:</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>53039880181, 5303 988 0181</li>\n        <li>53039700163, 5303 970 0163</li>\n        <li>53039900181, 5303 990 0163</li>\n        <li>53039800181, 5303 980 0181</li>\n        <li>53039700181, 5303 970 0181</li>\n        <li>53039900163, 5303 990 0181</li>\n        <li>53039880163, 5303 988 0163</li>\n        <li>53039800163, 5303 980 0163</li>\n        <li>53039700118, 5303 970 0118</li>\n        <li>53039800118, 5303 980 0118</li>\n        <li>53039880118, 5303 988 0118</li>\n        <li>53039900118, 5303 990 0118</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h4>O.E.M Numbers:</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>11657647003, 7647003</li>\n        <li>11657600890, 7600890</li>\n        <li>11657565912, 7565912</li>\n        <li>11657595678, 7595678</li>\n        <li>11657455912, 7455912</li>\n        <li>11657595351, 7595351</li>\n        <li>11657600881, 7600881</li>\n        <li>V755569780-04, 0375R4</li>\n        <li>7565424-01, 7565424-02</li>\n        <li>1165756542401, 756542401</li>\n        <li>1165756542402, 756542402</li>\n        <li>1165756542403, 756542403</li>\n        <li>1165756542404, 756542404</li>\n        <li>7565424-03, V75556978004</li>\n    </ul>\n\n</div>\n",
